**Wallet Recovery**

| Recovery Method | Process | Best For |
|----------------|---------|----------|
| Cloud Recovery | Encrypted key backup to Google Drive. User authenticates with Google → retrieves encrypted backup → decrypts with PIN/password → wallet restored | Consumer users who want simple self-service recovery |
